org.cytoscape.work.Task
public class DynForceLayoutAlgorithmTask<T>
extends org.cytoscape.view.layout.AbstractLayoutTask

DynForceLayoutAlgorithmTask is responsible for the generation of force-based network dynamics by associating to each nodes in the network appropriate intervals of node positions, which are stored in DynLayout.
